Why JAVA:
    It is compiled and interpreted language both.
    It is object oriented language.
    It is platform independent language. as JAVA compiler converts the code into "bytecode" which can be run on any platform.

JVM: Java Virtual Machine
    -> It is a software program that runs Java programs on a computer.
    :: Verifier, Class Loader, Method Resolver, Bytecode Interpreter, Native Method Interface, Garbage Collector.